libpocsag (1.0.2-1) stable; urgency=low

  * FSK modulator and demodulator with voice-band tones
  * Baseband NRZ output for FM transmitter / multimon-ng
  * RTL-SDR receiver (pocsag_sdr) with async IQ reader
  * Adaptive squelch for persistent-carrier repeaters
  * 500ms silence lead-in for receiver squelch
  * 65 tests, valgrind clean, zero allocation

 -- Brian <brian@example.com>  Wed, 02 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000

libpocsag (1.1.0-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Add FSK modulator and demodulator for full audio pipeline
  * Add baseband NRZ output for FM transmitter / multimon-ng use
  * Fix POCSAG numeric BCD encoding
  * Support sample rates: 8000, 16000, 32000, 48000 Hz
  * Support baud rates: 512, 1200, 2400
  * Frequency validation and per-instance thread safety documented
  * 63 tests, valgrind clean, zero allocation

 -- Brian <brian@example.com>  Mon, 30 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000

